Operations

TransducerTimeDataFields getFields()

Gets the fields of this TransducerTimeData object.

Return Value

TransducerTimeData object fields

void setFields(TransducerTimeDataFields fields, FieldNameList fieldNames)

Updates the fields of this TransducerTimeData object. If one or more fields are specified, only the fields listed will be updated, the other fields will be left unchanged. If the field list is empty ALL fields will be updated. The available fields are:

  • Transducer
  • Sensor
  • Node
  • Orientation
  • Amplification
  • Channel
  • Filter
  • StartTime
  • Status

Parameters

fields
updated fields structure
fieldNames
a string list with field names to be updated
